1. Privacy Policy
i. Scope
This “REALITY” Privacy Policy for iOS (this “Policy”) provides for the handling of
            personal information on the “REALITY” application (the “App”) provided by [REALITY, Inc.] (the “Company”).
            With regard to matters that are not provided for in this Policy, please also review the “
Basic Policy regarding the Protection of
              Personal Information
.” In addition, "8. Terms for specific Countries" applies to customers residing in
            the United States and South Korea.
2. Collection of Personal Information; Purpose of Use
i. Collection of facial expression data
In order to make the avatar work, this App will use TrueDepth API provided by Apple
            Inc. to collect facial expression data, but it will not be used for any purpose other than to make the
            avatar work, and the Company will not store the data or share it with any third party.
ii. Acquisition of Phone Numbers
The App will acquire and use your phone number for the purpose of logging in and
            displaying your REALITY account as a recommended user to other users. You can set whether or not to be
            displayed as a recommended user within the App.
iii. Retrieval of contacts data registered on the device
The App provides a function that allows a customer to upload the contacts on the
            customer's device, and if there is a user using the App in the contacts, this user can be displayed as a
            recommended user in the App. This functionality is only available when the customer uploads the contacts,
            and accesses and obtains the names and phone numbers (including information of individuals who are not users
            of the App) registered in the contacts on the customer's device.
The contacts information obtained by this function will be used only for the purpose of displaying
            recommended users within the App.
ⅳ. List of other information that will be collected
The Company may collect the following information from you in connection with the
            provision of the App:
< The information you directly provide to the Company >
Nicknames, self-introductions and images on your profile
Date of birth
Phone number
Name
Country and Region
Email Address
Contacts data registered in the device (name and phone number)
Information provided by you when making an inquiry
