7. Administration Policy
ⅰ. Amendment of this Privacy Policy
The terms of this Privacy Policy may be revised or amended. Unless otherwise
            specified by the Company, the revised or amended Privacy Policy will come into effect when it is posted on
            the App.
ⅱ. Retention Policy
Except as the case being necessary for the compliance of applicable law, regulation
            or order by the government, court, or other applicable authority, the personal data will be deleted when the
            personal data becomes unnecessary to achieve the purpose of use as specified in Section 2 ⅲ.
In addition, the user's account and information associated with the account will be deleted upon the customer's request for deletion. However, the following data will be retained after deletion, subject to security control measures.
Information to be retained
Usage of this application and the content of communication made within this application
Information provided by you when you contact us
Device information and identifiers
Reason for keeping
To comply with applicable laws, regulations, and to  respond to orders from government, court, or other regulatory agencies
ⅲ. Others
Please note that if you do not provide the Company with the latest and accurate
            information of yourself, you may not receive appropriate service.
