2.7 Use of Cookies
(1) About Cookies
We use cookies to provide you with a convenient website experience,
          and you have the right to refuse them. Cookies are very small text files that are sent to your
          computer by the server used to operate the website and stored on your computer's hard disk.
          Therefore, you can choose your own settings regarding the collection of cookies, so refusal to collect them.
          However, if you choose to refuse the storage of cookies, your use of some of our services may be limited.
(2) Purpose of Use of Cookies
We use cookies for the following purposes
To perform automatic login on REALITY for Web
(3) How to refuse cookies
