(2) The Company will use personal information within the retention period and usage
            period of personal information that the customer agreed to when using the App. If you withdraw your consent
            to the acquisition and use of your personal information, we will destroy your personal information without
            delay upon the achievement of the purpose of use or the expiration of the period of time for which such
            information is required.
